Invocation Name: magic conch
des:
The magic conch shell from Spongebob as an Alexa Skill! It pairs perfectly with Alexa's voice. Don't expect much positivity from the almighty magic conch shell. You can ask it anything really. Just say "Alexa, ask magic conch to answer my question [insert question]".

Ask it whatever you want and it will give you an answer. Future updates in store to replicate repeated no answers for "can I eat something?" and nothing for "what do we need to do to get out of the kelp forest?"
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
